Program: Omnibus
Title: Tunnels, Trees and Tactics
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lcw
Last Broadcast Date: 13 December 1996
Road protestors angry about the impact of road building on the environment explain why they built a complex series of tunnels in the path of a new extension to the A30 road in Fairmile, Devon. Contributors include from Daniel Hooper aka Swampy.